Package com.gtnewhorizon.structurelib.structure

package com.gtnewhorizon.structurelib.structure
This package provide support for multiblock structure checking.

All public stuff in this package and its subpackages are considered part of the public API. Backwards compatibility is maintained to the maximum extend possible.
